<P>THE CHARTER Granted by their MAJESTIES King WILLIAM And Queen MARY, TO THE INHABITANTS OF THE PROVINCE OF THE Massachusets-Bay, IN NEW-ENGLAND.</P>
<P>PRINTED at <HI>London,</HI> and Re-Printed at <HI>Boston,</HI> in <HI>New-England,</HI> By <HI>Benjamin Harris,</HI> Over-against the <HI>Old-Meeting-House.</HI> 1692.</P>
